450639d7-5a77-4900-8c49-a61314bc589b.description: Applies an impulse to players relative to what way the pad is facing.
450639d7-5a77-4900-8c49-a61314bc589b.title: Boost Pad

539e2ec8-cc49-484c-9d88-6e1cc6bbddc4.description: Players can swing off of them to gain height. You can only paint this part by clicking on the base of it.
539e2ec8-cc49-484c-9d88-6e1cc6bbddc4.title: Monkey Bar

1c16ae84-26e6-4bf5-b4be-dc45448e0b89.description: Players attach themselves to this part by standing in front of the side which has protruding bricks. The controls are the same as swimming, other than space. Instead of ascending, you can boost yourself off of the wall.
1c16ae84-26e6-4bf5-b4be-dc45448e0b89.title: Climbable wall plate

3bbe152e-3658-442d-95c7-35e17d48affb.description: Players attach themselves to this part by standing in front of the side which has protruding bricks. The controls are the same as swimming, other than space. Instead of ascending, you can boost yourself off of the wall.
3bbe152e-3658-442d-95c7-35e17d48affb.title: Climbable wall cylinder

f14cc68d-7653-41f5-bf9f-3d87c1a4e71d.description: A button that activates for a few seconds upon being shot with a spudgun/hit with the hammer.
f14cc68d-7653-41f5-bf9f-3d87c1a4e71d.title: Projectile/Melee button

c804d559-a4ac-44e2-a703-4dd709c4db14.description:
A part that teleports every player to a given location once they enter a certain radius around the part. 
Note: the Axis Visualization only works if you have the particle quality set to high!
c804d559-a4ac-44e2-a703-4dd709c4db14.title: Player Teleporter
